column6: Baron Zemo takes his battle against the new Captain America to a new and terrifying level.  And neither Bucky Barnes, or the readers will believe Zemo's last page revelation!  By the senses-shattering team of Ed Brubaker and Butch Guice! Rated T  ...$3.99
